<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   PHOENICIAN-SHIPS (Undated) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Oct. 10.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-10-10-98 1405EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
