 &QL; 
 &QL; 
HKN-KINGS (Edmonton, Alberta) _ Los Angeles Kings open season at
Edmonton Oilers, 7 p.m. &QL; 
By Roger Phillips/Long Beach Press-Telegram. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.) &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
BBO-McHALE-COLUMN (undated) _ Weekly baseball column. &QL; 
By Matt McHale. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
