   -- Notable: Chiefs have won three straight in series, with last
two decided by 7 points or fewer. ... Starting QB Elvis Grbac
(shoulder) returns for Kansas City after missing four games. ...
New England has won 14 of 18 at home and QB Drew Bledsoe is 25-15
at Foxboro Stadium. ... Chiefs are 5-0 when RB Donnell Bennett
scores and 69-4 in '90s when they have at least 30 carries. ...
Patriots have a return for a touchdown in three straight games, and
would tie NFL record with one today.
</P>
<P>
   -- Favorite: New England by 3.
</P>
