1990, with QB Kordell Stewart among five lowest-rated passers. ...
Pittsburgh is 40-6 under Cowher when it has individual 100-yard
rusher. ... Bengals WR Carl Pickens has 51 catches for 678 yards in
seven games against Pittsburgh.
</P>
