zero interceptions. ... Saints are tied for second in NFL with
plus-18 in turnover differential. ... New Orleans held Niners RB
Garrison Hearst to just 82 yards in 1997. ... Young and WR Jerry
Rice need two scoring hookups to become most prolific battery in
league history.
</P>
